document.title: unkey.dev
document.description: Unkey is an open source API Key management solution. It allows you to create, manage and validate API Keys for your users. It’s built with security and speed in mind.

body.raw:
[![](https://unkey.dev/images/landing/app.png)](https://unkey.dev)

Unkey is an open source API Key management solution. It allows you to create, manage and validate API Keys for your users. It’s built with security and speed in mind.
